        {type:"mc",q:"\"En aquella época no había teléfonos móviles\" describes:",opts:["A past situation or condition","A completed event","A future plan","A present fact"],ans:"A past situation or condition",hint:"The imperfect describes how things were, not what happened at one moment."},
        {type:"drag_fill",hint:"Fill in the classic imperfect trigger phrase and the habitual marker.",s:"{1} era niño, {2} los días jugaba en el parque.",blanks:{"1":"Cuando","2":"todos"},pool:["Cuando","todos","Ayer","cada"]},
        {type:"mc",q:"Which time expression does NOT typically trigger the imperfect?",opts:["Ayer a las tres","Todos los días","Cada verano","Normalmente"],ans:"Ayer a las tres",hint:"A specific time yesterday points to a completed, one-time action."},
        {type:"fb",opts:["época","día","vez","hora"],hint:"Which word completes the phrase meaning 'in those days'?",s:"En aquella {1}, la vida era muy diferente.",a:"época"}
